thread.title_full: SelectQuote Auto & Home reviewed by Dolores

author: Dolores
title: Dolores
text: I was hesitant about using an organization such as this as I believed that there would be hard sells or it would be a waste of time. I was pleasantly surprised. The representative was easy to work with and knew her stuff plus I saved over $200.00 a year on my homeowner's insurance.
